# Institutional-memory artifacts (extracted from source xlsx) are committed even
# though .data/ is otherwise ignored. Git can't re-include files inside an
# ignored directory directly; the un-ignore-then-re-ignore-contents dance below
# is required. See #34 (kicks).
!apps/api/.data/
apps/api/.data/*
!apps/api/.data/kicks-master-list.json
